lenders.name: LLL Team Fund
lenders.loan_because:
This fund is managed by members of the Late Loaning Lenders Team for the purpose of supporting loans that are on the verge of expiring. We lend to help avoid expiry without regard to gender, region, sector or loan terms. This is in keeping with the team philosophy of every loan deserving to be raised.

We welcome donations in the form of Kiva Gift Certificates which you can send by email to kiva.lll.fund@gmail.com. These donations are not tax-deductible.
Money in the fund cannot be withdrawn.

lenders.name: Amélie
lenders.loan_because:
Seule, je ne peux rien faire contre la guerre, la pauvreté et la maladie dans le monde. Néanmoins, en finançant de petits projets menés par des groupes de femmes, je participe concrètement à l'amélioration de leurs conditions de vie. Et si ces changements peuvent permettent ne serait-ce qu'à un seul enfant de grandir en étant nourri, scolarisé et en se sentant en sécurité, ma vie aura un peu plus de sens.

**************

Alone, I can do nothing against war, poverty and disease in the world. However, by funding small projects run by groups of women, I actually take part in the improvement of their living conditions. And whether these changes can help even only one child to grow up being fed, educated and feeling safe, my life will make a little more sense.
